org.mini2Dx.core.di.annotation

Annotation Type Prototype


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Prototype
    Marks a class as a prototype bean. All prototype beans are backed by a pool of prepared instances that are removed from the pool when the bean is requested. Removed instances are then replaced with new instances generated by another thread.
